episodes.title: 2 new batches of Epstein files include unsealed grand jury transcripts
episodes.description:
New files were released on Saturday from the cache of documents connected to convicted, and now deceased, sex offender Jeffrey Epstein. But most of what people were hoping to see in the files is still not included.

Read more: https://abc7.com/18302721/

episodes.title: Leaders of CA religious group charged with 2 murders over 13-year span
episodes.description:
The leaders of a mysterious religious organization based in Hemet are accused of murdering a 4-year-old boy in Colton as well as a 40-year-old man reported missing in Redlands.

Daryl Muzik Martin, 58, and his wife Shelly Kathryn Martin, 62, are charged with first-degree murder in the deaths of Timothy Thomas in 2010, and Emilio Ghanem in 2023.

READ MORE: https://abc7.com/post/leaders-hemet-religious-group-charged-2-murders-13-year-span/18290074/

episodes.title: Leaders of CA religious group arrested in connection with former member's disappearance
episodes.description:
The leaders of a Hemet religious group have been arrested in connection with the disappearance a Nashville man who was last seen more than two years ago.

Emilio Salem Ghanem was reported missing in May 2023 after visiting a Starbucks in Redlands.

Darryl Muzic Martin, 57, and his wife, Shelly Bailey "Kat" Martin, 62, were arrested earlier this month on illegal weapons charges after police served a search warrant at the Laguna Hills Lodge in Laguna Hills.

Ghanem had been a member of "His Way Spirit Led Assemblies," a religious organization based in Hemet that was led by the Martins, according to police.

READ MORE: https://abc7.com/post/emilio-salem-ghanem-missing-person-case-leaders-hemet-religious-group-arrested-connection-mans-disappearance/17666152/
